    <li>Please note that no booking fee is payable for any tickets purchased in person at any of our cinemas, including at automated ticket machines on the premises. The price paid in the cinema (at the cinemas listed in paragraph 1) for full priced standard tickets (excluding the tickets detailed in paragraph 3) will be more expensive than the price paid online.</li>
    <li>The total price paid for tickets purchased online for film screenings at the cinemas listed at paragraph 1 will be cheaper than the identical ticket purchased through the Booking Line.
